emlinux is the Linux kernel based embedded OS.
embox is used as the bootloader for emlinux.

emlinux kernel requirenments:
    For SPARC LEON 3: linux-2.6.21.1.tar.bz2
    For MicroBlaze: linux-2.6.33.tar.bz2

Download the kernel sources manually or rely on the build script.

Usage:
    Select arch:
	make menuconfig
    For build file system root tree:
	make users
    For build linux kernel (only after "make users"):
	make kernel
    For build images (only after "make kernel"):
	make image

Requirenments:
    patch < 2.6

